OL,6,FHouse prices fell by 2.3 per cent last
OL,7,Fmonth, marking the biggest monthly drop
OL,8,Fsince the 2008 financial crisis,
OL,9,Faccording to Halifax.
OL,11,FThe annual rate of house price growth
OL,12,Fslowed last month to 4.7 per cent, from
OL,13,F8.2 per cent in October with the
OL,14,Faverage UK house price standing at
OL,15,F#285,579 ` down from #292,406 in
OL,16,FOctober.
OL,18,FHalifax said the month-on-month drop
OL,19,F"reflects the worst of the market
OL,20,Fvolatility over recent months".
OL,3,CHouse prices take biggest tumble since
OL,4,C2008 crisis
